OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA chilly start this morning but
OL,6,Fwith plenty of sunshine. A little
OL,7,Fcloud may build during the day but it
OL,8,Fwill remain dry throughout. Feeling a
OL,9,Flittle fresher than Monday.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA dry and clear evening will
OL,12,Flead to a chilly night with a patchy
OL,13,Frural frost. Cloud will tend to build
OL,14,Flater in the night, especially across
OL,15,Fthe south.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FA dry and clear evening
OL,18,Fwill lead to a chilly night with a
OL,19,Fpatchy rural frost. Cloud will tend to
OL,20,Fbuild later in the night, especially
OL,21,Facross the south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
